reviewText: This imported Italian Blu-ray set contains 3 films: Meet the Parents, Meet the Fockers and Little Fockers. Overall, the picture and audio quality are fairly average and somewhat disappointing (Meet the Parents and Meet the Fockers need a good remastering). There are roughly 3 hours of total bonus content and 3 audio commentaries. The first two films are absolutely hilarious (4 stars overall) but Little Fockers pales in comparison and this entire collection could have been more deluxe so I rate this release only 2 stars. If you own the DVDs or stand-alone Blu-rays I would say don't bother importing this set because the overall quality and extras haven't been upgraded from previous releases. Region 2/B digital copy codes do not work in the US.Language: English, ItalianSubtitles: ItalianSpecial Features:[Meet the Parents] 2 audio commentaries + 1 hour of bonus content[Meet the Fockers] 1 audio commentary + 53 minutes of bonus content[Little Fockers] 59 minutes of bonus content
summary: Biggest Focker Collection 3-Disc Italian Blu-ray Collection
